### Test Order APIs

### 1. Create Order
POST https://localhost:7001/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "orderDate": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z",
  "orderDetails": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 2,
      "unitPrice": 25.50
    },
    {
      "productId": 2,
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 15.75
    }
