}

### 2. Get All Orders
GET https://localhost:7001/api/orders

### 3. Get Orders by Customer
GET https://localhost:7001/api/orders?customerId=1

### 4. Get Orders by Date Range
GET https://localhost:7001/api/orders?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-01-31

### 5. Get Order by ID
GET https://localhost:7001/api/orders/1
